Class Database

    android.content.ComponentCallbacks, android.content.ComponentCallbacks2

    public class Database
extends android.app.Application
    Database object used as an interface between our applications and our Firebase Real-Time database Important Note: Any method that gets an object from the firebase will not work due to the nature of threads. Copy and alter code, inserting into the actual activity.
